================================================================
                      ECLib - E-comOS Common Library
                          Oct , 28 2025
                       E-comOS Kernel Mode Team
=================================================================
The ECLib is a C Library for E-comOS , because E-comOS are not a 
Unix-Like system , so , something must ourself to created or did.
EClib is a MAIN REPO for basic link library , some library is created
in other repo such as TGlib
=================================================================
How to use it 
-----------------------------------------------------------------
This is ECLib , its means it is installed in your E-comOS , its not
support to user cause users cannot use it in thier work.
If you wannt "When the main process exits, you also want the sub-process
in the background not to be killed.",you can use this library such as